data.description: Discover your dream home in this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath Ranch!  As you arrive, you will be greeted by a welcoming, covered front porch.  Inside you will find a kitchen that boasts stainless steel appliances and elegant formica countertops that can be found in the kitchen and bathrooms.  The wood laminate floors extend throughout the main living areas of the home.  Outside you will find a large privacy fenced backyard that backs to the woods, offering a perfect sanctuary with added privacy.  There's even Gutter Guard gutters, a handy shed with electric, a fire pit and a back patio, perfect for barbecues and entertaining.  Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity!
